comments: Gallinari (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Bridges' (PHX) path and absorbs the contact.
Crowder (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Young (ATL).
Bogdanovic (ATL) moves somewhat laterally toward Crowder (PHX) and, after absorbing the initial body contact, cleanly dislodges Crowder of the ball at the end of the drive.
Paul (PHX) has a grasp of Bogdanovic's (ATL) right arm at the end of the drive and quickly releases as marginal contact occurs.
Capela (ATL) and Bogdanovic (ATL) maintain legal guarding positions as they trap Paul (PHX) along the sideline.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (ATL) path and absorbs the contact.
Gallinari (ATL) avoids making contact with Bridges' (PHX) head during the dunk attempt.
Crowder (PHX) and Gallinari (ATL) engage and disengage with one another as Gallinari moves to set the pick.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (ATL) path and absorbs the contact.
Bogdanovic (ATL) moves forward toward Booker (PHX) and marginal body contact occurs after Booker receives the pass.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Bogdanovic's (ATL) path and absorbs the contact.
Ayton (PHX) places his hands to Capela's (ATL) side and marginal contact occurs as Capela moves to contest the driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) moves alongside Booker's (PHX) path and absorbs the marginal body contact made after Booker's gather.
Gallinari (ATL) rests his hand on Ayton's (PHX) side and marginal contact occurs during Ayton's put-back attempt.
Booker (PHX) and Bogdanovic (ATL) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Bogdanovic (ATL) places his hands to Bridges' (PHX) back and marginal contact occurs as Bogdanovic naturally releases away.
Capela (ATL) slightly extends his hands on Booker's (PHX) back and marginal contact occurs as Capela begins to roll out of his screening position.
Ayton (PHX) moves somewhat laterally toward Young (ATL) and marginal body contact occurs prior to Young's gather.
Young (ATL) brings his off-arm to Ayton's (PHX) left leg and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Ayton (PHX) is moving forward toward Young (ATL) and marginal body contact occurs prior to Young losing control of the ball during the driving shot attempt.
Huerter (ATL) and Paul (PHX) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Huerter (ATL) extends his right hand forward and brushes Paul's (PHX) right arm as he is passing.
Gallinari (ATL) moves forward into Crowder's (PHX) space and initiates contact with Crowder that affects his follow-through.
Craig (PHX) initiates contact with Young's (ATL) side/arm after his gather and affects his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Crowder (PHX) has his hand on Gallinari's (ATL) right hip and marginal contact occurs before Crowder releases.
Craig (PHX) legally contests Bogdanovic's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
